title: Suits TV Show Soundtrack - All Music - USA
description:
All of the music played on USA Network's television series "Suits". I have included all music featured on every episode to date. That means music from S1E1 through S3E1. There's songs from Harvey's record player, the opening and closing theme songs, and many many more from throughout the show. I included as many as I could find... Enjoy!

There's 93 songs total.
